dc_description_s: Historical City of Houston parcels, joined with land use table data.This data is part of the 2003 City of Houston GIS Release 9 available in the GIS Lab in Rotch Library.  The land use table (luse.dbf) contains more historical information not visible here, and is available on CD in the MIT GIS lab. Later City of Houston GIS releases also contain historical land use information, which may include updated information for 2003. Other releases available in the Rotch GIS Lab are 1998, 2000, 2002 and 2004.
dc_publisher_s: Houston (TX) Planning and Development Department, IT Division
